summary: Dan and Phil rize stream notes 26/7/18 live at 21:17 on the tour bus not moving cute mumbling  phil loves their accents its...
body:
Dan and Phil rize stream notes 26/7/18

live at 21:17

on the tour bus

not moving

cute mumbling 

phil loves their accents

its slightly laggy

everyone nealry died bc phil didnt like how hot it was

sleepless night w/ phil in the bus is a maybe

lagging again

phil has terrible sleep on the bus

aye the winners

its lagging rly bad

20 sunglasses winners, 10 videos and 1 switch

its so bad help

10 videos, 10 polaroid photos signed and 10 painting(?)

on abt chicago pizza

dan moaned abt the crust

drink goes everywhere

they have a snack cupboard

a new dnpg videos w/ flaming hot cheetos

Said something abt muse and they didnt rly like the song(?) 

excited for the album

dans fortune cookie

Dan”its your front bottom” in reference to fortune cookie

gaming video

fanny packs and bumbags

it keeps freezing end me

sofa crease

spon

end
